chunk_content: The following represents the Minimum Package for other post-GBV care services that V must be in place to count under this indicator: E N • Provision of Clinical Services: (all the following must be in place and available to count persons— T independent of whether people use the specific service) I O • Rapid HIV testing with referral to care and treatment as appropriate (Please note that individuals N should also be counted under the MER HIV testing and counseling indicator (i.e., # of individuals who received HIV testing and counseling services and received their results).
